Changelog:

###Scripts version 2461### / Date: 16.01.2026 / Download update size: 4 megabytes
* fixed creating prefix backup
* added path selection for the .exe file if there is no shortcut (when launched from https://ppdb.linux-gaming.ru)

###Scripts version 2460### / Date: 12.01.2026 / Download update size: 4 megabytes
* the "EMULATORS" tab is disabled by default (can be enabled in the global settings)
* audio driver switching has been moved from the global settings (user.conf) to the individual game settings
* translations have been updated

###Scripts version 2459### / Date: 12.01.2026 / Download update size: 4 megabytes
* added the ability to apply settings and launch the game from the report page at https://ppdb.linux-gaming.ru
* added replacement of your username with xuser when creating a log
* fixed path detection when launching .ppdb files if there is more than one executable file or the name contains spaces
* uses an empty dxvk.conf for optiscaler (replaces the default one in PP)

###Scripts version 2458### / Date: 11.01.2026 / Download update size: 4 megabytes
* disabled DXVK_HUD display in-game when creating a log
* added the ability to launch .ppdb game settings files (for future integration with https://ppdb.linux-gaming.ru)
* added display of the URL to the settings file (if downloaded from https://ppdb.linux-gaming.ru)

###Scripts version 2457### / Date: 10.01.2026 / Download update size: 60 megabytes
* updated optiscaler to version 0.9.0-pre8 (thanks to @eljeyna)

###Scripts version 2456### / Date: 09.01.2026 / Download update size: 230 megabytes
* updated PROTON_LG to version "10-28"
* updated versions:
    - DXVK_NEW_VER "2.7.1-355" (shared with dxvk-nvapi)
    - VKD3D_NEW_VER "1.1-4981" (shared with vkd3d-shader)
* updated DOTNET prefix (750 MB)
* disabled frame limiting when the "USE LS FRAMEGEN" frame generator is enabled (use the in-game frame limiter)
* minor CLI fixes for PortProtonQT (thanks to Boria138)
* fixed Windows Steam - uses WINE_LG by default
* disabled shortcut creation for uninstall.exe

